COPY_EXISTING ~C0D2_A0.SPL~ ~OVERRIDE~
SAY NAME1 ~Totemic Guardian~
SAY UNIDENTIFIED_DESC ~The totemic druid is persistently guarded by an animal spirit, which manifests when an enemy is within range of the totemic druid and remains until the battle ends. The spirit animal can be controlled, increases in power as the summoner gains in druid levels, and provides the totemic druid with persistent bonuses unless the spirit is destroyed in battle. The totemic druid may select a spirit animal to be guarded by once per day, with each providing different bonuses.
  BEAR'S ENDURANCE: The summoner gains a +10% bonus to physical resistances and a +1 bonus to Saving Throws vs. Death.
  WOLF'S TENACITY: The summoner gains a +10% bonus to all damage dealt, with an additional +1 bonus to melee damage.
  LION'S COURAGE: The summoner gains a +1 bonus to THAC0, Morale and Saving Throw vs. Spells.
  SNAKE'S SWIFTNESS: The summoner gains a +1 bonus to Armor Class, Movement Rate and Saving Throws vs. Breath.~

